thy of becoming the lord''s successor. \n\nWhile the two share different goals, they agree to help each other in order to reach them. Kumatetsu searches for recognition; Ren, now known as Kyuuta, searches for the home he never had. As the years pass by, it starts to become apparent that the two are helping each other in more ways than they had originally thought. Perhaps there has always been less of a difference between them, a boy and a beast, than either of the two ever realized.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "broadcast": {"day": null, "time": null, "string": null, "timezone": null}, "favorites": 3229, "licensors": [{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/producer/102/Funimation", "name": "Funimation", "type": "anime", "mal_id": 102}], "producers": [{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/producer/53/Dentsu", "name": "Dentsu", "type": "anime", "mal_id": 53}, {"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/producer/76/Yomiuri_Telecasting", "name": "Yomiuri Telecasting", "type": "anime", "mal_id": 76}, {"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/producer/113/Kadokawa_Shoten", "name": "Kadokawa Shoten", "type": "anime", "mal_id": 113}, {"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/producer/245/TOHO", "name": "TOHO", "type": "anime", "mal_id": 245}, {"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/producer/1003/Nippon_Television_Network", "name": "Nippon Television Network", "type": "anime", "mal_id": 1003}, {"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/producer/1912/Arquebuse", "name": "Arquebuse", "type": "anime", "mal_id": 1912}], "relations": [{"entry": [{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/manga/87921/Bakemono_no_Ko", "name": "Bakemono no Ko", "type": "manga", "mal_id": 87921}, {"url": "https://myanimelist.net/manga/89988/Bakemono_no_Ko", "name": "Bakemono no Ko", "type": "manga", "mal_id": 89988}], "relation": "Adaptation"}, {"entry": [{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/31108/Green_Dakara_x_Bakemono_no_Ko", "name": "Green Dakara x Bakemono no Ko", "type": "anime", "mal_id": 31108}], "relation": "Othe